        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p>You can use your nanites to create the perfect tool for a job. Outside of combat, you can have your nanites form a toolkit of a level no higher than half your level (minimum 0). The item lasts for 1 minute. Because your nanites must be actively working to provide the tool, you can't use other feats that require the use of your nanites while you're using them as a tool.</p>"
